  <entry>
    <title>GroupBy - 資料分群的收納師</title>
    <url>/2024/03/17/Therapy-for-Our-Data-LINQ-GropuBy/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="MS-Doc-名詞解析"><a href="#MS-Doc-名詞解析" class="headerlink" title="MS Doc 名詞解析"></a>MS Doc 名詞解析</h2><p><code>keySelector</code> : 要使用什麼屬性(or欄位)做分組 </p>
<p><code>comparer</code>： 客製的等值比較器，這裡是比較key是否相同來決定要不要分在同一組</p>
<p><code>elementSelector</code> : 參數是針對分組中的元素,使用前還沒有得到分組後的結果</p>
<p><code>resultSelector</code> : 參數是針對分組結果再進一步進行資料結構的轉換</p>
<p><code>IEnumerable&lt;System.Linq.IGrouping&lt;TKey,TSource&gt;&gt;</code> : 分組後的資料</p>
<p><code>IEnumerable&lt;TSource&gt;</code> : 資料源</p>
<h2 id="MS-Doc-範例"><a href="#MS-Doc-範例" class="headerlink" title="MS Doc 範例"></a>MS Doc 範例</h2><p>這個情境會對分組後的資料動手腳,就不需要在後面處理<br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/2BeCpkd.png" alt="Image"><br>在此,GroupBy只把所需的名字抓出來，所以在做處理時不用再從Pet中找出Name資料了，相對精簡<br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/q4IOyAZ.png" alt="Image"></p>
<h2 id="情境一"><a href="#情境一" class="headerlink" title="情境一."></a>情境一.</h2><p>按價格範圍對訂單進行分組</p>
<figure class="highlight csharp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Main</span>()</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    List&lt;Order&gt; orders = <span class="keyword">new</span> List&lt;Order&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">new</span> Order &#123; OrderId = <span class="number">1</span>, TotalAmount = <span class="number">150</span>m &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">new</span> Order &#123; OrderId = <span class="number">2</span>, TotalAmount = <span class="number">50</span>m &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">new</span> Order &#123; OrderId = <span class="number">3</span>, TotalAmount = <span class="number">20</span>m &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">new</span> Order &#123; OrderId = <span class="number">4</span>, TotalAmount = <span class="number">500</span>m &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">new</span> Order &#123; OrderId = <span class="number">5</span>, TotalAmount = <span class="number">80</span>m &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">new</span> Order &#123; OrderId = <span class="number">6</span>, TotalAmount = <span class="number">200</span>m &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">new</span> Order &#123; OrderId = <span class="number">7</span>, TotalAmount = <span class="number">700</span>m &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">var</span> groupOrders = orders.GroupBy(order =&gt; </span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> order.TotalAmount <span class="keyword">switch</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">decimal</span> amount <span class="keyword">when</span> amount &lt; <span class="number">100</span> =&gt; <span class="string">&quot;Small Order&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">decimal</span> amount <span class="keyword">when</span> amount &gt;= <span class="number">100</span> &amp;&amp; amount &lt;= <span class="number">500</span> =&gt; <span class="string">&quot;Medium Order&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            _ =&gt; <span class="string">&quot;Large Order&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;);</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">foreach</span>(<span class="keyword">var</span> <span class="keyword">group</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> groupOrders)</span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">group</span>.Key.Dump();</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">foreach</span>(<span class="keyword">var</span> order <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="keyword">group</span>)</span><br><span class="line">		&#123;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="string">$&quot;OrderId : <span class="subst">&#123;order.OrderId&#125;</span>, TotalAmount : <span class="subst">&#123;order.TotalAmount&#125;</span>&quot;</span>.Dump();</span><br><span class="line">		&#125;</span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>.Dump();</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Order</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="built_in">int</span> OrderId &#123; <span class="keyword">get</span>; <span class="keyword">set</span>; &#125;</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="built_in">decimal</span> TotalAmount &#123; <span class="keyword">get</span>; <span class="keyword">set</span>; &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
